thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Richard D

author: Richard D
title: Richard D
text: Have used Ink Station site over the years for many orders. Each transaction was attended to very quickly, mostly delivered next day. The products represent quality even though not using the recommended (approved) Brand. Cost is very economical. Happy to recommend Ink Station as a reliable and trustworthy company.
